data.description: WELCOME to a stunning two-bedroom condo located in Jennings Point with PRESERVE VIEWS. One of the standout features of this condo is FRESHLY PAINT, NEW CARPET, adding warmth and character to the space. Both bedrooms are spacious and bright, with plenty of natural light and walk-in closets. As part of the Oakleaf community, residents have access to amenities including clubhouses, pools, recreation centers, fitness centers, sports fields, and playgrounds. The community is also conveniently located near entertainment, shopping, and restaurants in Oakleaf Town Center. Assigned Parking Space #445 Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful two-bedroom condo your new home!
